  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "\n<p><b>Type:</b> Genjutsu (Phantasm)</p>\n<p><b>Rank:</b> 6 (Spell Level 3)</p>\n<p><b>Chakra Cost:</b> 8</p>\n\n<p><b>Learn DC:</b> 20 | <b>Successes:</b> 3</p>\n<p><b>Perform:</b> 8 | <b>Perform DC:</b> 21</p>\n\n<p><b>Components:</b> F, H</p>\n\n<hr>\n\n<p>Creatures within the area see a gigantic ball of fire descending from the sky, engulfing their surroundings in fire and brimstone. Creatures caught in the area who fail their save take 3d8 damage, and will take 1d6 damage each round they remain within the area as they see their surroundings set ablaze. This damage cannot reduce creatures below 0 HP, but those brought to 0 HP by the technique's damage will be @Condition[unconscious]{unconscious} for 1d4+2 hours or until healed.<br><br>Creatures immune to fire are unaffected, as are creatures that cannot use their sense sight, smell, touch and hearing. Creatures warned about the technique's effects will receive a +8 bonus on their save to resist it (identifying it does not grant this bonus).<br><br>This technique can be dispelled.</p>\n\n\n\n",
      "summary": "",
      "instructions": ""
    },
